title: My Apartment Tour | Dixie D'Amelio
author: Dixie D'Amelio
description:
Welcome or welcome back to my channel! My apartment tour is finally here!! I'm so excited to share this tour with you all. Since I moved, I've been working really hard to turn this apartment into a home and and I'm so happy with how everything turned out. Thank you to everyone that helped me turn my apartment into my dream home. Thanks so much for watching!
